      <link>https://rahulkrrrishna.xyz/blog/2024-01-01-loading-vs-fetching/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 2024 11:15:00 +0530</pubDate>
      <guid>https://rahulkrrrishna.xyz/blog/2024-01-01-loading-vs-fetching/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h3 id=&#34;the-basics&#34;&gt;&#xA;  The Basics&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#the-basics&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;No Data + Fetching Data = LOADING&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Yes Data + Fetching Data = FETCHING&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;why&#34;&gt;&#xA;  Why?&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#why&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;As long as the data we have is not invalid. We have no reason to hide it away from the user.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;examples-from-around-the-world&#34;&gt;&#xA;  Examples from around the world&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#examples-from-around-the-world&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Loading | Fetching&#xA;&lt;img src=&#34;https://rahulkrrrishna.xyz/images/loading-vs-fetching/Untitled%206.png&#34; alt=&#34;YouTube Loading State&#34;&gt; YouTube Loading State |&lt;img src=&#34;https://rahulkrrrishna.xyz/images/loading-vs-fetching/Untitled%207.png&#34; alt=&#34;YouTube Fetching State&#34;&gt; YouTube Fetching State&#xA;&lt;img src=&#34;https://rahulkrrrishna.xyz/images/loading-vs-fetching/Untitled%208.png&#34; alt=&#34;Apollo App Loading State&#34;&gt; Apollo App Loading State | &lt;img src=&#34;https://rahulkrrrishna.xyz/images/loading-vs-fetching/Untitled%209.png&#34; alt=&#34;Apollo App Fetching State&#34;&gt; Apollo App Fetching State&#xA;&lt;img src=&#34;https://rahulkrrrishna.xyz/images/loading-vs-fetching/Untitled%2010.png&#34; alt=&#34;Fotmob Loading State&#34;&gt; Fotmob Loading State | &lt;img src=&#34;https://rahulkrrrishna.xyz/images/loading-vs-fetching/Untitled%2011.png&#34; alt=&#34;Fotmob Fetching State&#34;&gt; Fotmob Fetching State&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Illusion of Touch</title>
      <link>https://rahulkrrrishna.xyz/blog/2023-11-27-illusion-of-touch/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 Nov 2023 11:15:00 +0530</pubDate>
      <guid>https://rahulkrrrishna.xyz/blog/2023-11-27-illusion-of-touch/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h3 id=&#34;til&#34;&gt;&#xA;  TIL&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#til&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;It&amp;rsquo;s physically impossible to touch anything because we&amp;rsquo;re made up of atoms. When we get too close to an object, our electrons and the electrons of that object will repel each other. However, our brain interprets the sensation of those repulsion forces as the illusion of &amp;ldquo;touch&amp;rdquo; even though they never actually touch.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
